com.launchdarkly.client

Class RedisFeatureStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.launchdarkly.client.RedisFeatureStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FeatureStore, java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class RedisFeatureStore
extends java.lang.Object
implements FeatureStore
    A thread-safe, versioned store for FeatureFlag objects backed by Redis. Also supports an optional in-memory cache configuration that can be used to improve performance.

        host - the host for the Redis connection
        port - the port for the Redis connection
        prefix - a namespace prefix for all keys stored in Redis
        cacheTimeSecs - an optional timeout for the in-memory cache. If set to 0, no in-memory caching will be performed
